---
title: Mexican Kidney Bean & Spinach Rice Bowl with Avocado Salsa & Sour Cream
description: We know bowls are a bit trendy right now, but this one is well deserving of its hip appearance. If you had Mexican relegated to junk food status, this nourishing version with fresh herbs and avocado is going to put it back on the menu! Everyone will love this warming bowl, packed with veggies and beans but full of flavour!
